      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i dont even recognize the person looking back. it feels like the real me, the one who actually had a life and dreams, died a long time ago. now im just... going through the motions. like a ghost just stuck in a body that doesnt belong to me anymore.",
